---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 30, 2026</p>
    <p>At time4, accessible from time4.pages.dev, your privacy is one of our main priorities. This document outlines the types of information collected and recorded by our site.</p>
    <h2>Information Collection & Use</h2>
    <p>We do not maintain a real-time user database server. Any processing of system settings or timing data occurs purely client-side or at the secure cloud network edge.</p>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may partner with third-party network providers and advertising ecosystems (such as Adsterra) to support development. These vendors use automated script cookies to tailor layout metrics on our platforms.</p>
</Layout>
